snippet.textDisplay: All coke studios are precious. They represent cultures in a modern way capturing the true magic of traditional songs. They make you think about cultures and countries in a different way,. Through their songs they express emotions, philosophy and the way of life of different people from different cultures and backgrounds. Their videography is also astounding.Many of the pictures when you pause this video is just wallpaper worthy. How do all the coke studios manage to capture their culture this way? It is like a form of art that is beautiful on its own. The term sound of magic is no joke and they prove that with every single song release. Words cannot describe how marvelous the coke studios are. Greetings and blessings from Bangladesh.
